snippet.title: Game Endeavor
snippet.description:
Howdy! And welcome to Game Endeavor. I'm developing "Zoe and the Cursed Dreamer". A 2D open world RPG, where you'll explore an immersive world, meet lovable characters, and live amongst them in your own home.

My main goal in making this channel is to create a strong tight-knit community. So leave comments and drop by the Discord to say hello. I look forward to hearing from you! Let us know what project piece of art you're working on. Our community is about sharing progress and growth.
